data.description: Priced to sell!  Very nice, well cared for home located in highly desirable Spanish Fork neighborhood. Close to schools, parks, and entertainment. Corner lot with fully fenced back yard. Cable tv and internet is available through Spanish Fork community network. Just minutes away from Spanish Fork golf course with easy access to I-15. Seller is offering $5,000 towards buyers closing cost, or VA assumability option @ 3.375% for those that are qualified. Call for details. Agent is related to the seller.
